# 💬 End-to-End Chat Application in C (Socket Programming)

A professional **multi-client chat application** built in **C** using **WinSock2** and **multithreading**.  
This project demonstrates real-time network communication, concurrency handling, and TCP socket programming — key system design and networking concepts used in real-world applications.

---

## 🧠 Overview
This project enables multiple clients to connect to a single server and exchange messages in real time.  
Each client runs on a separate thread, while the server efficiently handles all connections concurrently.

---

## 🚀 Key Features
- 🔗 **End-to-End Chat System** — Server + multiple clients  
- 🧵 **Multi-threaded Server** — Supports up to 100 concurrent users  
- 💬 **Real-time Message Broadcasting**  
- 🔒 **Thread-safe Communication** with synchronization  
- ⚙️ **Lightweight, Efficient, and Built in Pure C**

